videos.description: Dawn Staley tells SEC Now South Carolina had to rely on its defense, which held Arkansas to .313 field-goal shooting, including 5 of 31 (.161) on threes.
videos.headline: Staley says Gamecocks survived being 'a little rusty'

videos.description: After piling up 17 points, 14 rebounds, five steals and three blocks in the win over Arkansas, Aliyah Boston says she just played "South Carolina basketball."
videos.headline: Aggressiveness led to Boston's huge game for Gamecocks
